            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};


var xcmap = null;

    xcmap = xc.initMap();

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>

    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};


var xcmap = null;
jQuery(document).ready(function() {
    xcmap = xc.initMap();
});

</script>

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};


var xcmap = null;
jQuery(document).ready(function() {
    xcmap = xc.initMap();
});

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>

            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>

            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>

            </li>

            </li>
            </ul>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};


var xcmap = null;
jQuery(document).ready(function() {
    xcmap = xc.initMap();
});

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};


var xcmap = null;
jQuery(document).ready(function() {
    xcmap = xc.initMap();
});

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>

            </li>

            </li>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};


var xcmap = null;
jQuery(document).ready(function() {
    xcmap = xc.initMap();
});

</script>

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>

{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};


var xcmap = null;
jQuery(document).ready(function() {
    xcmap = xc.initMap();
});

</script>

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};


var xcmap = null;
jQuery(document).ready(function() {
    xcmap = xc.initMap();
});

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            
            <table id='map-table'>
            <tr>
            <td id='map-cell'>
            <div id='map-canvas'></div>
            </td>
            <td>
            <div class='map-sidebar'>
            
            <h3>Map Legend</h3>
        
            <div class="map-legend">
                <h4>Subspecies</h4>
                <ul><li><span class="marker-image"><img class="icon" src="/static/img/markers/b-14.png" /></span> <span class="marker-text"><a href='/species/Scytalopus-latrans?query=ssp:%22eastern+form%22'>eastern form</a></span></li><li><span class="marker-image"><img class="icon" src="/static/img/markers/c-14.png" /></span> <span class="marker-text"><a href='/species/Scytalopus-latrans?query=ssp:%22eastern+form%2Fsubcinereus%22'>eastern form/subcinereus</a></span></li><li><span class="marker-image"><img class="icon" src="/static/img/markers/d-14.png" /></span> <span class="marker-text"><a href='/species/Scytalopus-latrans?query=ssp:%22intermedius%22'>intermedius</a> &middot; <span class='authority'>Zimmer, JT, 1939</span></span></li><li><span class="marker-image"><img class="icon" src="/static/img/markers/a-14.png" /></span> <span class="marker-text"><a href='/species/Scytalopus-latrans?query=ssp:%22latrans%22'>latrans</a> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></span></li><li><span class="marker-image"><img class="icon" src="/static/img/markers/f-14.png" /></span> <span class="marker-text"><a href='/species/Scytalopus-latrans?query=ssp:%22ssp.+nov.%22'>ssp. nov.</a></span></li><li><span class="marker-image"><img class="icon" src="/static/img/markers/g-14.png" /></span> <span class="marker-text"><a href='/species/Scytalopus-latrans?query=ssp:%22subcinereus%22'>subcinereus</a> &middot; <span class='authority'>Zimmer, JT, 1939</span></span></li><li><span class="marker-image"><img class="icon" src="/static/img/markers/h-14.png" /></span> <span class="marker-text"><a href='/species/Scytalopus-latrans?query=ssp:%22subcinereus%2Feastern+form%22'>subcinereus/eastern form</a></span></li></ul><h4>Unclassified</h4>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};


var xcmap = null;
jQuery(document).ready(function() {
    xcmap = xc.initMap();
});

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};

    xcmap = xc.initMap();

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};

    xcmap = xc.initMap();

            <h1>Blackish Tapaculo &middot; <span class='sci-name'>Scytalopus latrans</span> &middot; <span class='authority'>Hellmayr, 1924</span></h1>
            
            <ul class='taxonomy order'>
            <li>Order: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?o=PASSERIFORMES'>PASSERIFORMES</a>
            <ul class='family'>
            <li>Family: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?f=Rhinocryptidae'>Rhinocryptidae</a> (Tapaculos)
            <ul class='genus'>
            <li>Genus: <a href='/explore/taxonomy?g=Scytalopus'>Scytalopus</a></li>
            <ul class='species'>
            <li>Species: <span class='sci-name'>latrans</span></li>
            </ul>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            </ul>

xc.initMap = function()
{
    try {
        var map = xc.createMap("map-canvas", "http://www.xeno-canto.org/ranges/Scytalopus_latrans.kmz?v=2", false);
        map.setMarkers(xc.initialMarkers.markers, xc.initialMarkers.specs, true);

        return map;
    } catch (e) {
        return null;
    }
};


var xcmap = null;
jQuery(document).ready(function() {
    xcmap = xc.initMap();
});
